		<description><![CDATA[Jeff Lefevere and I return to review the top wine stories of the past month including tongue-twisting wine names, a disturbing wine manifesto, trends in wine marketing, the stellar 2009 Bordeaux vintage and much more. Hosts: Tim Elliott and Jeff Lefevere Topics If the wine is hard to pronounce, is it worth more? Has wine [...]<p><a href="http://winecast.net/2012/02/26/tmiw-2-the-tastes-they-are-a-changin/">TMiW 2 &#8211;  The Tastes They Are A-Changin&#8217;</a> originally appeared on <a href="http://winecast.net">Winecast</a>. Licensed under <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/us/" target="_blank">Creative Commons</a>.</p>
