			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>It&#8217;s rare when network TV and wine come together but when it does I take a look. I&#8217;m not a regular viewer of Undercover Boss but might be after this episode at Kendall-Jackson Wine Estates. New President Rick Tigner works at the bottom of this organization and learns a lot. And he does the right thing after these experiences.</p>
<p>K-J is a very savvy marketing organization and in one episode really humanizes the brand. I think they will sell a lot of wine this week as a result.</p>
